<body>
  <header class="main-header">
    <div class="main-header__wrapper">
      <div class="main-header__content">
        <h1 class="main-header__title">Preco</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="app">
    <main class="app__body">
      <div class="splash-screen">
        <div class="splash-screen__overlay">
          <h1 class="splash-screen__title">Preco{{#if debug}} - DEBUG{{/if}}</h1>
          <p class="splash-screen__strap-line">Every box counts</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="section-header" id="project-section">Projects</h2>
      <div class="project-section">
        <div class="project-section__project">
          <div class="project-section__image-wrapper">
            <h3 class="project-section__title">Norwegian Fjords</h3>
          </div>

          <div class="project-section__info">
            <p class="project-section__blurb">
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vivamus imperdiet pretium velit sit amet cursus. Pellentesque felis mauris, elementum id libero ac, euismod convallis massa. Aliquam erat volutpat. Praesent quis lorem in diam facilisis consequat vel in metus. Maecenas vitae dolor ut sem ultricies pulvinar eget a orci.
            </p>
            <p class="project-section__blurb">
              Nunc nec sollicitudin diam, et finibus sem. Etiam pharetra augue in commodo condimentum. Vestibulum ac erat nec velit eleifend laoreet. In sed iaculis nibh.
            </p>
            <div class="project-section__links">
              <a class="project-section__link">Contacts <i class="project-section__link-icon far fa-angle-right"></i></a>
              <a class="project-section__link">Website <i class="project-section__link-icon far fa-angle-right"></i></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-section__project">
          <div class="project-section__image-wrapper">
            <h3 class="project-section__title">Aalesunds FK</h3>
          </div>

          <div class="project-section__info">
            <p class="project-section__blurb">
              Morbi placerat orci ut ligula euismod accumsan. Sed vestibulum massa eros, id lacinia ipsum placerat ut. Morbi volutpat tortor tellus, at sodales diam feugiat et. Praesent consectetur in diam eget molestie. Sed egestas ullamcorper lacus non ultricies. Ut interdum pellentesque tempus. Vivamus et pretium arcu. Quisque auctor lacinia tempus. Donec id ex risus. Fusce sodales bibendum nibh nec ultricies. Maecenas sed faucibus turpis. Curabitur bibendum ultrices iaculis.
            </p>
            <div class="project-section__links">
              <a class="project-section__link">Contacts <i class="project-section__link-icon far fa-angle-right"></i></a>
              <a class="project-section__link">Website <i class="project-section__link-icon far fa-angle-right"></i></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- END ==> project-section -->


      <h2 class="section-header" id="contact-section">Contacts</h2>

      <div class="contact-section">
        <div class="contact-section__contact-list">
          {{#each primaryPeople}}
            <div class="contact-section__contact">
              <div class="contact-section__contact-image-wrapper">
                <img class="contact-section__contact-image"
                    src="{{ this.thumb }}"
                    alt=""
                    role="presentation">
              </div>

              <div class="contact-section__contact-details">
                <p class="contact-section__contact-detail contact-section__contact-detail--name">
                  {{ this.name }}{{#if this.isUser}} - You{{/if}}</p>
                <p class="contact-section__contact-detail contact-section__contact-detail--role">
                  {{#if this.role }}
                    {{ this.role }} at
                  {{/if}}
                  {{ this.company.name }}</p>
                {{#if this.phone_1 }}
                  <p class="contact-section__contact-detail contact-section__contact-detail--phone-1">
                    {{ this.phone_1 }}</p>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if this.phone_2 }}
                  <p class="contact-section__contact-detail contact-section__contact-detail--phone-2">
                    {{ this.phone_2 }}</p>
                {{/if}}
                <a class="contact-section__contact-detail contact-section__contact-detail--email"
                  href="mailto:{{ this.email }}">
                  {{ this.email }}</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          {{/each}}

          {{#times 2}}
            <div class="contact-section__contact contact-section__contact--padder"></div>
          {{/times}}
        </div>

        {{#if user.loggedIn}}
          <div class="contact-section__contact-list">
            {{#each nonPrimaryPeople}}
              <div class="contact-section__contact">
                <div class="contact-section__contact-image-wrapper">
                  <img class="contact-section__contact-image"
                      src="{{ this.thumb }}"
                      alt=""
                      role="presentation">
                </div>

                <div class="contact-section__contact-details">
                  {{#if ../user.isAdmin}}
                    <button class="contact-section__delete-contact"
                            onclick="if(confirm('Are you sure you want to delete this person?')){location.href='/delete-person/{{ this.id }}'}">x</button>
                  {{/if}}
                  <p class="contact-section__contact-detail contact-section__contact-detail--name">
                    {{ this.name }}{{#if this.isUser}} - You{{/if}}</p>
                  <p class="contact-section__contact-detail contact-section__contact-detail--role">
                    {{#if this.role }}
                      {{ this.role }} at
                    {{/if}}
                    {{ this.company.name }}</p>
                  {{#if this.phone_1 }}
                    <p class="contact-section__contact-detail contact-section__contact-detail--phone-1">
                      {{ this.phone_1 }}</p>
                  {{/if}}
                  {{#if this.phone_2 }}
                    <p class="contact-section__contact-detail contact-section__contact-detail--phone-2">
                      {{ this.phone_2 }}</p>
                  {{/if}}
                  <a class="contact-section__contact-detail contact-section__contact-detail--email"
                    href="mailto:{{ this.email }}">
                    {{ this.email }}</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            {{/each}}

            {{#times 2}}
              <div class="contact-section__contact contact-section__contact--padder"></div>
            {{/times}}
          </div>
        {{/if}}
      </div>
      <!-- END => contact-section -->


